_sText:
Many hours were spent on this map, it's pretty well balanced but has some flaws along with a few texture errors but nothing huge.

Enjoy.

--------------------

FY_Wideout (6-32)
Keegan Penney – KeeganPenney@hotmail.com
==================================

Fy_wideout carries a design heavily based on fy_iceworld but set in a tunnel themed tactical environment. 

Armaments:

-2 of every primary weapon except only 1 AWP in both Terrorist and Counter-Terrorist spawns.

-2 DEagles in both spawns accompanied by 2 smoke grenades in both spawns.

==================================
Thanks to:

Interlopers.net mapping community – it wouldn’t look as good without them.

Alminie_Manhunter – credit is due for helpful advice.
